title: Nominations and Withdrawal Sent to the Senate | The White House
content: NOMINATION SENT TO THE SENATE:     Kurt Campbell, of the District of Columbia, to be Deputy Secretary of State, vice Wendy Ruth Sherman, resigned.WITHDRAWAL SENT TO THE SENATE:     Laura Daniel-Davis, of Virginia, to be an Assistant Secretary of the Interior, vice Joseph Balash, resigned, which was sent to the Senate on January 23, 2023.# # #
